CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1962, pg. A9 reads: "IOTA Honorees - Mrs. Katie E. Johnson (left), Eastern regional director of the Iota Phi Lambda Sorority, and a past president of Pi Chapter, makes a presentation to Mrs. Marian Bryant, while Mrs. Florence Ball Jones (right), president of Pi Chapter, presents a gift to Mrs. Virginia M. Gittens. Mmes. Bryant and Gittens were honored at a Business Week smorgasbord, last Saturday, at the Eastern Star home on Brushton Ave. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Iota Phi Lambda Sorority members, from left: Katie E. Johnson, making presentation to Marian Bryant, and Florence Ball Jones, presenting gift to Virginia M. Gittens, posed behind table in Eastern Star home, Brushton Avenue
